<footer id="contactar" class="bg-gray-50 pt-16 pb-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Brand and Search -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <!-- Logo Icon -->
          <div
            class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="currentColor"
              class="w-5 h-5 text-white"
            >
              <path
                d="M11.47 3.84a.75.75 0 011.06 0l8.69 8.69a.75.75 0 101.06-1.06l-8.689-8.69a2.25 2.25 0 00-3.182 0l-8.69 8.69a.75.75 0 001.061 1.06l8.69-8.69z"
              ></path>
              <path
                d="M12 5.432l8.159 8.159c.03.03.06.058.091.086v6.198c0 1.035-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875H15a.75.75 0 01-.75-.75v-4.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-3a.75.75 0 00-.75.75V21a.75.75 0 01-.75.75H5.625a1.875 1.875 0 01-1.875-1.875v-6.198a2.29 2.29 0 00.091-.086L12 5.43z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">EnVenta</span>
        </div>

        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Si quieres promocionar tu producto o servicio y aún no sabes cómo,
          puedo ayudarte a crear una página clara, moderna y orientada a
          resultados, como esta. Escríbeme directamente y cuéntame sobre tu
          proyecto.
        </p>

        <div
          class="flex max-w-md bg-white p-1.5 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200"
        >
          <div class="flex-1 flex items-center px-3">
            <!-- Icono ubicación (puedes cambiarlo si quieres) -->
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 mr-2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H4.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 6.75m19.5 0l-9.75 6.75L2.25 6.75"
              ></path>
            </svg>

            <!-- Input bloqueado -->
            <input
              type="email"
              value="ernesto134alonso123@gmail.com"
              readonly
              class="w-full bg-transparent text-slate-700 text-sm focus:outline-none cursor-default"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Botón email -->
          <button
            class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white px-4 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-colors cursor-pointer"
            aria-label="Enviar correo"
            onclick="window.location.href='mailto:ernesto134alonso123@gmail.com'"
          >
            <!-- Icono email -->
            Enviar
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Spacer -->
      <div class="hidden lg:block lg:col-span-3"></div>

      <!-- Links Columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Products -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Tambien hacemos</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li>
              <span
                class="text-slate-500 hover:text-emerald-600 text-sm transition-colors"
                >Web Apps</span
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <span
                class="text-slate-500 hover:text-emerald-600 text-sm transition-colors"
                >Mobile Apps</span
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <span
                class="text-slate-500 hover:text-emerald-600 text-sm transition-colors"
                >Desktop Apps</span
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <span
                class="text-slate-500 hover:text-emerald-600 text-sm transition-colors"
                >Consultoria</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Follow us -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Síguenos</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li>
              <a
                href="https://www.facebook.com/marketplace/item/1313330097501410"
                class="flex items-center text-slate-500 hover:text-blue-600 text-sm transition-colors gap-3"
              >
                <svg
                  class="w-5 h-5"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  ><path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M22 12c0-5.523-4.477-10-10-10S2 6.477 2 12c0 4.991 3.657 9.128 8.438 9.878v-6.987h-2.54V12h2.54V9.797c0-2.506 1.492-3.89 3.777-3.89 1.094 0 2.238.195 2.238.195v2.46h-1.26c-1.243 0-1.63.771-1.63 1.562V12h2.773l-.443 2.89h-2.33v6.988C18.343 21.128 22 16.991 22 12z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
                >
                Facebook
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Bar -->
    <div
      class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-slate-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4"
    >
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
        &copy; 2025 EnVenta. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a
          href="#"
          class="text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-600 text-xs transition-colors"
          >Privacy Policy</a
        >
        <span class="text-slate-300">|</span>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="text-slate-400 hover:text-emerald-600 text-xs transition-colors"
          >Terms of Service</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
